原为一间寿司吧设在科威特。它的灵感在传统的日本料理，他们的高品质标准。我们的品牌塑造建议保持这种古典文化，由复古意象代表的一些细节。黑色笔触的侵入一些抵押品设计代表了主人，一位年轻的科威特，这也是主要的厨师。他的教育和人才让他提供一个真正的产品，同时他施加他的特殊风格的每一个菜谱上。

我们用“Kintsugi”的餐具，修复破碎的陶器与粉状金，银或铂的日本工艺。

单色配色方案，阿拉伯文和日文排版的选择，并且构成了字笔触“RAW”共享一个男性化的个性是由他们所提供的菜肴美味反击。

原文：

&nbsp;

Raw is a sushi bar located in Kuwait. It is inspired on the traditional Japanese cuisine and their high quality standards. Our branding proposal keeps some details of this classical culture, represented by the vintage imagery. The black brushstrokes that invade some of the collateral design represents the owner, a young Kuwaiti that is also the main Chef. His education and talent allows him to offer an authentic product while he imposes his particular style on every recipe.

We used “Kintsugi” for the tableware, a Japanese technic of repairing broken pottery with powdered gold, silver, or platinum.

The monochromatic color scheme, the Arabic and Japanese typography selection, and the brushstrokes that form the word “RAW” share a masculine personality that is countered by the delicacy of the dishes they offer.

&nbsp;

